dct_title_s: Albania: roads / compiled and drawn in the Branch of Research and Analysis, OSS. (Index)
dct_description_sm: Map is number 2599. 6 October 1943. "Reliability code 1A-2B-2." Ancillary map: "Roads according to terrain types traversed," showing five classes of roads. Verso: index. Map shows route numbers and five classes of roads. "Confidential."
dct_creator_sm: United States. Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C.] : Office of Strategic Services, Branch of Research and Analysis, 1943.
